Grails Ki Plugin

Creators:
Originally developed by Peter Ledbrook
Port and additional development undertaken by Bradley Beddoes @ Intient - http://intient.com

License: 
Apache 2.0

Overview
This plugin extends on work done for JSecurity in Grails and integrates the API of Apache Ki (name is soon to change as asvised by Apache Incubator when a final project name is known this will change here).

Currently a work in progress, see the example application for details.
